    vmc orgs sddc templates: list

    List all available SDDC configuration templates in an organization

    Request:

    HTTP request

    GET https://{server}/rest/vmc/api/orgs/{org}/sddc-templates

    Path Parameters

    Name Type Description
    Required
    org string Organization identifier. (required).

    Response:

    HTTP Status Code: 200
